Package: helloJavaWorld
Type: Package
Title: Tutorial for building wrappers from Java to R
Version: 0.1
Author: Ana Valdivia
Maintainer: Ana Valdivia <avaldivia@ugr.es>
Description: The package we will create in this tutorial, the helloJavaWorld package, will invoke a very simple Java class, 
             the HelloJavaWorld class, from inside an R function of the package, the helloJavaWorld function.
Depends: R (>= 2.7.0), rJava (>= 0.5-0)
SystemRequirements: Java (>= 7.0); 
